.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Rider / VS Code

.idea/
.vscode/

## Logs

*.log

## OS files

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Environment files

.env

## ASP.NET Core

appsettings.Development.json

## Publish output

publish/

## NuGet

*.nupkg
packages/
.nuget/

## Entity Framework migrations (optional)

# Uncomment if you don't want migrations

# Migrations/

## SQLite database files (optional)

*.db
*.sqlite

## IIS Express

iisexpress/

## Resharper

_ReSharper*/
*.DotSettings.user

## Coverage reports

coverage/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## Temporary files

*.tmp
*.temp

## Node (if frontend added later)

node_modules/
dist/
build/

## Mac/Linux hidden files

.*.swp
